Protocol HDCP (model series 2011) hex (decimal) codes:

POWER     - 0x08 (8)

Energy    - 0x95 (149)
AV        - 0x30 (48)
INPUT     - 0x0B (11)
TV/RAD    - 0xF0 (240)

0         - 0x10 (16)
1         - 0x11 (17)
2         - 0x12 (18)
3         - 0x13 (19)
4         - 0x14 (20)
5         - 0x15 (21)
6         - 0x16 (22)
7         - 0x17 (23)
8         - 0x18 (24)
9         - 0x19 (25)

LIST      - 0x53 (83)
Q.VIEW    - 0x1A (26)
VOL+      - 0x02 (2)
VOL-      - 0x03 (3)
FAV       - 0x1E (30)
RATIO     - 0x79 (121)
MUTE      - 0x09 (9)
CH+       - 0x00 (0)
CH-       - 0x01 (1)

MENU/HOME - 0x43 (67) / 0x23 (35) (keep pressed 5sec)
WIDGETS   - 0x58 (88) (only US models)
NETCAST   - 0x59 (89)
Q.MENU    - 0x45 (69)
3D        - 0xDC (220)

RIGHT     - 0x06 (6)
LEFT      - 0x07 (7)
UP        - 0x40 (64)
DOWN      - 0x41 (65)

OK        - 0x44 (68)

BACK      - 0x28 (40)
GUIDE     - 0xA9 (169)
EXIT      - 0x5B (91)

RED       - 0x72 (114)
