YELLOW    - 0x63 (99)
BLUE      - 0x61 (97)
3D setup  - 0x61 (97)

TEXT      - 0x20 (32)
T.OPT     - 0x21 (33)
SUBTIT    - 0x39 (57)

LIVE TV   - 0x9E (158) (for DVR to return to live feed if paused or re-winded)
REC       - 0xBD (189) (only on DVR models)
STOP      - 0xB1 (177)
PLAY      - 0xB0 (176)
PAUSE     - 0xBA (186)
<<        - 0x8F (143)
